template(name="gaWhyCareModal")
    div.modal(id="why-care-modal")

        div(style="color:rgba(0,0,0,.54);background:rgba(0,0,0,.03); padding:15px;")
            h4.left-align
                | Share the infomation with your potential participants

        div.modal-content
            p(style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500;") 1. Who are you? (e.g. I am a Kombucha community member in San Diego...)
            textarea.materialize-textarea(id="why-care-first-question" class="textarea-comment why-care-questions" name="feedback" placeholder="{{hasFirstShareInfo}}" required)
            p(style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500;") 2. What would the world learn? (e.g. The world will learn the benefits of drinking Kombucha, for example, it is a rich source of probiotics...)
            textarea.materialize-textarea(id="why-care-second-question" class="textarea-comment why-care-questions" name="feedback" placeholder="{{hasSecondShareInfo}}" required)
            p(style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500;") 3. Expected time taken for participant? (e.g. 10 minutes per day.)
            textarea.materialize-textarea(id="why-care-third-question" class="textarea-comment why-care-questions" name="feedback" placeholder="{{hasThirdShareInfo}}" required)
            a.btn.light-blue.darken-4#save-whyCare-btn(href="#" class="disabled") Save your answers
        div.modal-footer
            a.gray-text(class="modal-action modal-close btn-flat") Close
